{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"41053-ka-kaa-ki-kee","title":"क का कि की","description":"यो किताप भर्खर पढ्न सुरु गरेका साना–साना नानीहरूका लागि तयार पारिएको हो । यसमा प्रस्तुत विषय, शैली र प्रस्तुति सहज,मीठो र सरल होस् भनेर सकेसम्म मिहिनेत गरिएको छ । खास गरेर हाम्रा नानीहरू आफैँ उत्साहित भई पढून् भन्ने उद्देश्यले नै यो तयार पारिएको हो ।\r\n\r\nकतै अप्ठेरो शब्द भेटिएमा आफ्ना बालबालिकालाई सघाउनुहुन गुरु तथा अभिभावकहरूसँग अनुरोध गरिन्छ । ","language":"Nepali","langCode":"ne","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Shantdas  Manandhar"],"illustrators":["Yuvaka  Srestha"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/41053-ka-kaa-ki-kee"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/103109/size3/207237416193614284e90e801f2972f4.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/103109/size6/207237416193614284e90e801f2972f4.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/96547/size6/32bde2d63bfeaa0c854ccc431bc28844.jpg","text":"क का कि की भित्र \nको को रहेछन् हेरौँ ?","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/96548/size6/16fec4d8bab51b9ba3e85685ced1866b.jpg","text":"क का कि की भित्र \nकाका छन् कि छैनन् ?","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/96549/size6/b6ba2ea3973caaa999f020c3e05cfa6c.jpg","text":"क का कि की भित्र \nकाका यता रहेछन् ।","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/96550/size6/8eb5e15e16e7f43617b58fc06d6d6579.jpg","text":"क का कि की भित्र \nकाकी छन् कि छैनन् ?","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https: